{"title": "Pursuit of God", "description": "\"As the heart panteth after the water brooks, so panteth my soul after thee, O God.\" This thirst for an intimate relationship with God, claims A.W. Tozer, is not for a select few, but should be the experience of every follower of Christ. But, he asserts, it is all too rare when believers have become conditioned by tradition to accept standards of mediocrity, and the church struggles with formality and worldliness. Using examples from Scripture and from the lives of saints who lived with this thirst for God, Tozer sheds light on the path to a closer walk with God. (Summary by D. Leeson)", "duration": 10404, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "2033", "name": "Aiden Wilson Tozer"}], "coverArt": "http://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt29/Pursuit_God_1302.jpg", "copyright_year": "1957", "genres": ["Christianity - Other"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "David Leeson"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "David Leeson"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Barry Eads"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "MaryAnn"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "00 - \tIntroduction/Preface", "readers": [2827], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/pursuit_of_god_1105_librivox/pursuitofgod_00_tozer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 490}, {"section": 1, "title": "01 - Following Hard After God", "readers": [2827], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/pursuit_of_god_1105_librivox/pursuitofgod_01_tozer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 916}, {"section": 2, "title": "02 - \tThe Blessedness of Possessing Nothing", "readers": [2827], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/pursuit_of_god_1105_librivox/pursuitofgod_02_tozer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 946}, {"section": 3, "title": "03 - Removing the Veil", "readers": [2827], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/pursuit_of_god_1105_librivox/pursuitofgod_03_tozer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1371}, {"section": 4, "title": "04 - \tApprehending God", "readers": [2827], "path": "http://www